name: Branislav Volčko
note:
Silvester Pullman wrote: "IT and programmers outsourcing- Peter Hofierka. Digital marketing and lead research- Juraj Bottlik", so I added new leads by his recommendation. Juraj Bottlik is interested in prices for Sales (lead generation managers (B2B), sales) and copywriters for social media. On December 15, he asked: "What would we get for the full-time role if we hire lead generation manager/sales? Could you be more specific about what we can expect? Thanks!". I replied: " If you hire lead generation manager/sales your work will be done. Our lead generation manager will increase your internal database with new clients, up to 80 connection requests per day. Also they are doing follow ups and emailing.". I also sent him a link to our presentation and told that we could arrange a call, so that Sales Department could tell him more details and answer all his questions. He has been ihnoring me, so on December 20, I wrote: "Hello, Juraj! I just wanted to ask, have you considered our offer? Are you interested in hiring?". He has been ignoring me for more than a week since this message and almost 2 weeks in general. Juraj Bottlik wrote: "Hello! I would like to move things further and setup a call to discuss everything on a more granular level and see if there is a suitable match according to what we need. Which date/time suits you the best? Thanks!"

Company Name:  Voltia 

Company Website:  https://www.voltia.com

Contact Person: Juraj Bottlik

Specialties: Logistics

Country: Slovakia 

Target Audience: worldwide

Immediate Requirement: They specializes in logistics, with primer markets in UK, Poland, Germany, Slovakia, Czech R (want to reach also Italy, Hungary). They are interested in remote sales people for prospecting and cold outreaching. They will train candidates and provide all needed information. Previously they hired someone for this role from Slovakia, but didn’t like the price and results, they need quality leads. He would like to have an interview with our candidates and their head of Sales department. Also Juraj was asking if it’s possible to deduct some amount from LG managers’ salaries if they will not provide the agreed amount of leads per day. 

Next Contact Date: he will inform us about date on Monday

Next step: sending email, f-up on Monday

SM Sveta (Ruzaliya)
